race.description: Bi-Rite Home Appliances Wangaratta Maiden Plate
race.comment: SILVER TOP RIDGE (11) led and missed a whisker here on debut and then resumed at Wodonga with a narrow defeat. Jumps ideally from the rails barrier and with the extra fitness will be tough to peg back. KILMER (1) resumes and won a recent jumpout at Echuca. Placed his only fresh outing and has pieces of form that stack up. Coffey's engagement suggests he's pleasing the yard. YELLOWKNIFE (12) debuts for a top metro stable and has won his last four jumpouts. Draws an inside barrier and if the money comes she's sure to feature. FROSTED AMBER (7) had been well-educated before her 3L defeat at Kyneton on debut. Has been kept on the fresh side and maps well enough.
